data.description: This Walbrook home is a semi detached town home. The home features a thoughtfully converted 2 bedroom 2.5 baths, with the half bath being located on the first level off the kitchen. Spacious living room, dining room and kitchen. This home has a front and back yard, with an inviting front porch and recently constructed rear upper and lower deck, overlooking a scenic park. A large primary bedroom with a walk-in closet and spacious bathroom, with a stand alone shower and separate tub. The second bedroom sits in the rear next to the second full bath and gives access to the above deck. This home is conveniently located near shopping, grocery, dining  parks and fitness center. This affordable gem awaits your personal touch to redefine as your own distinctive haven. OPEN HOUSES SATURDAY 2/24 AND SUNDAY 2/25 1-4
